  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/71e81a1051a5c0e3365e03d20b0f2cc2.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After accidentally shooting an angel out of the sky, you—a cynic who doesn't believe in love—are forced to shoulder the angel's mission of helping the couples of the world. While the angel believes that love will always bring happiness, it falls upon you to decide.<br><br>The relationships you encounter are never that simple, and the question of what is ultimately best for all involved only grows more complex with each one. So you must decide if each love is truly worth rekindling, and live with the consequences of your decision. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What do you believe will lead to the most happiness?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/71c7b1c4bdeb56fc4eced1933029ca3a.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=344 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/ffa5db869592bf22f455c75439a58097.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=1765 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/071426f49f0b2249fa48c656726a9cee.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Star-Crossed Classmates</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Love Forged Over The Internet</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Couple Forced To Choose Between Their Love And Their Dream</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three More Tenuous Pairings, Plus Your Own With Each Heroine!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/b48997d92f68576322be8b077384febd.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The best choice is rarely clear, and mostly subjective. There are always consequences in either case, and an emotional ride is all that's guaranteed.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/eeda542043a101e1843e4bf39d9e0dbf.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience unforgettable tracks, including 9 vocal songs composed by the rockstars at OVERDRIVE.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/71e81a1051a5c0e3365e03d20b0f2cc2.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After accidentally shooting an angel out of the sky, you—a cynic who doesn't believe in love—are forced to shoulder the angel's mission of helping the couples of the world. While the angel believes that love will always bring happiness, it falls upon you to decide.<br><br>The relationships you encounter are never that simple, and the question of what is ultimately best for all involved only grows more complex with each one. So you must decide if each love is truly worth rekindling, and live with the consequences of your decision. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What do you believe will lead to the most happiness?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/71c7b1c4bdeb56fc4eced1933029ca3a.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=344 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/ffa5db869592bf22f455c75439a58097.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=1765 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/071426f49f0b2249fa48c656726a9cee.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Star-Crossed Classmates</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Love Forged Over The Internet</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Couple Forced To Choose Between Their Love And Their Dream</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three More Tenuous Pairings, Plus Your Own With Each Heroine!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/b48997d92f68576322be8b077384febd.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The best choice is rarely clear, and mostly subjective. There are always consequences in either case, and an emotional ride is all that's guaranteed.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668360/extras/eeda542043a101e1843e4bf39d9e0dbf.avif?t=1769906825\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience unforgettable tracks, including 9 vocal songs composed by the rockstars at OVERDRIVE.</p>",
